N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4121.4 - False protest

State Regulations

Any person found guilty of protesting a horse falsely and
without cause or merely with intent to embarrass a race, shall be punished as
provided by this Subchapter. Notes
